cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC

This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on language modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of different representations, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves experiments and comparisons of different methods, which could fall under cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
